    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and it's honestly such a gem. It\u2019s been well-loved and is in great shape, running super smoothly and looking sharp. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a reliable, comfortable car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
